le=\"Samsung Galaxy S25\" target=\"_blank\"\u003e\n\t\t\t\tSamsung Galaxy S25\n\t\t\t\u003c/a\u003e\n\t\t\n\t\u003c/h5\u003e\n\n                                                    \n                \t\n                \n\n                \n                \n                \n                \n\n                \n                                    \u003cp\u003e$600 \u003cspan\u003e$800\u003c/span\u003e Save\n                        $200 \u003c/p\u003e\n                \n                                    \u003cp\u003eSamsung\u0026#39;s Galaxy S25 keeps things small without sacrificing power. With a Snapdragon 8 Elite processor, 12GB of RAM, and all sorts of tools courtesy of Galaxy AI, this is everything you expect from a modern flagship squeezed into a relatively svelte chassis.\u003c/p\u003e\n                \n                \t\n\n\n                \n\n                \n                \n                \n            \u003c/div\u003e\n                \n        \n        \n                    \n        \n            \u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n                    \n                        \u003cli\u003e        \n    \n                                \n        \n                            \n                                                            \n                                                                                                                \n            \n    \n                                        \n    \n        \n    \n        \n                \n        \n    \u003cdiv data-include-community-rating=\"false\" id=\"7809-428c-b7668502dbbf\" data-nosnippet=\"\"\u003e\n        \n        \n                            \n                        \t\n\t\u003cdiv data-img-url=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/s25-plus-square.png\" data-modal-id=\"single-image-modal\" data-modal-container-id=\"single-image-modal-container\" data-img-caption=\"\u0026#34;\u0026#34;\"\u003e\n\n            \n\n\n\n\n\u003cfig